So the story gets told in 5 parts.
First part will be to get known the city and how the heroine gets there.
Second part will be the introduction of the white witch and how she terrorizes the city.
Third part will be the start of the quest to save the city, a quest that starts simple, but get filled with mystery.
Fourth part will include her friends that they help her to find what is hidden in Helius.
Last part will be fighting the white witch with the cape.

So in total there will be
1 main character
2 submain character
1 quest giver
1 white witch
several other npcs that hand over the quest items and story and such.